Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:36.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Are you really planning to cross this lake, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.58,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,440)\fs48}The Burning Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.58,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,478)\fs35}-Luffy's Side-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:37.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:41.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And just {\i1}how{\i0} are you planning to cross this lake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:43.84,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Parts of it are on fire.  Others are frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:47.57,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Then the water temperature might be fine.\NAnd I am quite sweaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:48.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Shall we swim across?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.22,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.16,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Me and Robin can't swim, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.61,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You want to ride us across, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Well, whatever I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:03.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If we don't cross the lake,\Nwe'll be taking a huge detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.79,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Guess there's no choice.  I'll handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.41,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.16,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Fan Grass
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.80,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What's this grass?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:26.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's a boat!  That's amazing, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.81,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And this fan grass will serve as oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.30,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,You have all sorts of seeds, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.71,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:38.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The Boyn Islands were a treasure trove\Nof strange plants, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:43.20,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Whenever I entered a dangerous area, \NI managed to snag some convenient plants!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I survived on that island for two whole years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,so you could say that there's nothing I can't han{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Get aboard, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.00,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,You'll get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey!  I was the one who made that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.13,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,To the land of shaved ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.36,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Row, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The wind is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And it's a headwind, at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.68,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:13.52,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The extreme temperature difference\Non the island causes the wind to blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.19,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,The water's boiling out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:19.12,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If we'd tried to swim, it would've been a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We're not really making much progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You have to row, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.49,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,You won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.27,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Wait, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.45,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.87,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,It's the centaur from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:36.11,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  Did you decide to join my crew after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.38,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Did you just invite him {\i1}again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Will you stop asking every freak we meet to join us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.88,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,A horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.09,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:49.93,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That reminds me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.70,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,didn't the Snail Phone say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.12,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,It's freezing... Is that you, boss? {Copy-paste from 579. Man, they sure don't get tired of flashing back to this conversation, do they?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:05:02.39,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,The intruders are heading your way!  Please take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:08.57,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Something just appeared on the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.18,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Is that his boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:24.75,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So the emergency transmission was from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:28.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nit would be silly for him to try to attack us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.96,Main,Boss,0,0,0,,One of them is carrying a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.16,Main,Boss,0,0,0,,Is that the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.14,Main,Boss,0,0,0,,samurai who cut down our comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.23,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,A volcanic eruption?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.27,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Visiting this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:51.87,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,makes me feel like Akainu and Aokiji are glaring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.79,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:55.87,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Let's just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.12,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Fire, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.01,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,A river!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.04,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Hey, that was amazing, Smokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:20.53,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Incredible!  How did you know\Nthere was a river behind the ice, Smokey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.40,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You really are great, Smokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.99,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,I didn't notice anything at all, Smokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.56,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,It was obvious to anyone watching the water currents!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.70,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,You lack basic observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.67,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Also, don't be so familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.54,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,But this creates a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.08,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:48.08,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,The issue isn't that there's a river here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:51.88,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,We should be asking,\Nwas the ice blocking this current natural...{ Btwb: "floes" is not a very common word, for me at least. Also, they looked more like ice bergs or masses of ice instead of detached sheets, which is what floes are, according to what I looked up. }
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.88,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,or was it placed intentionally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.89,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.20,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,someone might have hidden it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:04.41,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You're saying that someone might live\Non this island, in this gas cloud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.60,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,No way!  They'd have to wear masks all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:11.30,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,The voice we heard in the transmission definitely said the name of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.84,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,We must have heard wrong, Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.55,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Even Snail Phones would die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.58,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.71,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,If you've got time to laugh, \Nthen you've got time to clear the next ice wall!{ Btwb: Note in case we stick with "floe". }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:31.54,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.89,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,A wall of ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:37.46,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,If we crash into that, the entire ship will sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.42,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.69,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Smash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.40,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:48.66,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,441)}The frozen lands - Inside the mysterious facility
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:48.66,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,480)}-Nami's Group-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This way, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You better run if you wanna get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.92,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You sure are fired up, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:04.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Of course I am!  Sanji gave me a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.98,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,to protect the children\Nand get them safely out of this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.39,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:14.87,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I will complete my mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.81,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,As the only man here, I must do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.92,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You should figure that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.32,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.78,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Lady, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.07,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:43.83,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I can't even count the number of times I've been in situations crazier than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.58,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Just follow me and don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.25,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:59.56,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(640,438)}Inside the mysterious facility - Biscuits Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:59.56,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(640,476)}-Sanji's Group-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.11,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.11,Main,Man,0,0,0,,H-He's installed weapons all over his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.01,Main,Man,0,0,0,,It must be him!\NThe one who destroyed the door to the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.87,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You seem interested in my weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.51,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Alright!  I'll show them to you as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.14,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Load your guns with poison gas bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.04,Main,Man,0,0,0,,There aren't any kids in the room anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.09,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Don't hold back, riddle him with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:44.64,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,In that case, let's remove your masks\Nso we can breathe the poison gas together!{ Btwb: Sanji's all about sharing! }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.51,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.60,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Don't be so anxious. { def: anxious? }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.27,Main,Man,0,0,0,,He got our masks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.78,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Our air tanks too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.53,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Don't fire the gas bullets! { def: way too late now, but shouldn't it be gas grenades? }{ Btwb: Mangarule has grenades, mangahere says shots, but they all work, really. }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.95,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.75,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Sheep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.90,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:20.69,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,This is unlike any man I have faced before! { def: intentionally not using gender neutral language for this guy }{ Btwb: Good call. Chauvinistic samurai is chauvinistic. }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.17,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Who could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:24.55,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I cannot seem to take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Seriously, what are you talking about?{ Btwb: Looked up "what are you on about?", urban dictionary was the first hit. I don't find Franky to be quite that urban, but mostly I don't think our audiance would think this as normal. Also, I wouldn't be saying "again" if I first asked what he was doing and then went to ask what he means. }
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.97,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I speak of my torso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:31.88,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:37.23,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,442)}Mysterious facility - Front Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:37.23,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,480)}-Brook-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.96,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey wait!  What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.74,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,W-W-Who are you, good sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.10,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What happened to your head and legs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:59.26,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Scary!  Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.26,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Fire!  Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.95,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,We'll soon be finished travelling this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.08,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,What lies ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:38.43,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,I have a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.81,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,By any chance... might you be... a ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.91,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If that is the case, isn't this inappropriate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.95,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It's midday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:58.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Haven't I always been good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:01.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I just came ashore to make snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:05.49,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Ah, if you like, shall we make some together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.92,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,If we work together,\Nwe might even be able to make a snow sculpt{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:15.89,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:20.73,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,That man has no eyes,\Nso how is he able to attack so accurately?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:28.11,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Though, come to think of it, I don't have eyes either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.59,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Scary!  Strong!  Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.66,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,What has gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:54.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,At least tell me why you're fighting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.85,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nitouryuu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.85,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,Two-Sword Style { tlc: Did we always use hyphens for this? }{ def: we've been horribly inconsistent with sword styles, it's hyphenated about half the time. i don't really have a preference, if no one else has a preference i'll prolly drop it }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.46,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Please, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.45,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Scary!  Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.16,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.49,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.84,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Did you catch the escaped prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.43,Main,Man,0,0,0,,No, I came to report on the G-5 ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.68,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Oh, them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.80,Main,Man,0,0,0,,The poison gas cloud didn't stop them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:49.68,Main,Man,0,0,0,,and at the moment, the warship\Nis using its cannons to destroy the ice walls,{ Btwb: floes }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.51,Main,Man,0,0,0,,and they're slowly making their way inland.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.72,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Before long, they'll reach this laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:02.07,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Why? Why do they go to such lengths\Nto land on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:06.00,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Did they get tipped off in some way? {Literally "Do they have some sort of conviction?"... Rather vague, really, so I may have misinterpreted it.}{ def: went with a reinterpretation of the manga's line: "Do they have some kind of knowledge of what lies ahead?" }
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.89,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Who is commanding the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.81,Main,Man,0,0,0,,It's Vice-Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.42,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Smoker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:18.32,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Of all people... What a troublesome man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:22.21,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Conceal the ships\Nthat are docked at the main entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.14,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Should we deal with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:27.14,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Nobody is allowed to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:30.18,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,so make sure they don't see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.67,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Then what about you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:35.25,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd!  There's no way I could go out there! { def: maybe "leave this place"? }
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.01,Main,Man,0,0,0,,But that leaves us with no way of stopping them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.97,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.14,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,There's no gas here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.42,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,It's true!  I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.69,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Then why was there all that gas before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.60,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,It must be the work\Nof someone who doesn't want us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.12,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Is there really someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.55,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Doctor Vegapunk's research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.40,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Or rather, it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:20.31,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be abandoned,\Nan empty building devoid of people or equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.32,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Who's been living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.65,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Hey!  Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:31.56,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!  Are you scared of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:35.08,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,There's no need to be polite and ring the doorbell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:38.92,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,We can open the door in no time\Nif we just blast it with the ship's cannons, Smokey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.87,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Uh, Smoker-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.60,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Hey, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.22,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:48.73,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You listenin'?!  This island is off-limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.12,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Whoever you are, you're under arrest, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.72,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,It's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.14,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You finally understand your situation?\NWe are the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:17.20,Main,Law,0,0,0,,What business do you have at my vacation home...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.37,Main,Law,0,0,0,,White Hunter? {So previously I've translated Law's whole thing with appending "-ya" to the end of people's names as him ending it with "-er"... This obviously does not work here, so... SPEECH-QUIRK IGNORED FOR THE TIME BEING.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.67,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.68,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:28.25,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Used to be a rookie with a 440 million Beli bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.67,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.31,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,alongside Hawk-Eye Mihawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:35.43,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,the Pirate Empress, Boa Hancock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.57,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Donquixote Doflamingo and the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:42.48,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,he is one of the Government-authorized pirates... the Seven Warlords of the Sea!{ Btwb: Either needs to be possessive (Government's authorized) or needs to be hypenated (government-authorized). }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.44,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.41,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:00.04,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,I don't want anything to do with that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.80,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,You know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.59,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,In order to become a Warlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:22.11,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,he delivered the hearts\Nof one hundred pirates to Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.94,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,He's completely deranged!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.73,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,He gives me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:32.20,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:39.37,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,This island is forbidden\Nto both pirates and the Government alike, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.83,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:50.10,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,442)}Inside Dr. Vegapunk's old laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:50.10,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,482)}-Nami's Group-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:49.44,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Daddy!  Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:59.46,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Hey, you said you weren't sick anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.64,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.18,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What disease did you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:06.41,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,None of you show any symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:13.39,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,I don't know.  They just said "You have a disease",\Nand "You'll be fine after a year".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:19.46,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,A disease that passes after a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:20.82,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:29.84,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,Mommy and Daddy asked some people to cure me\Nand then those people took me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:33.41,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,So, your parents told you to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.63,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.24,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,It was those people,\Nthey told me all of this outside of my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.06,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,and then I was taken here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:44.69,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,They said that I could've infected Mommy and Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.49,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,I didn't even get to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.18,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Was it like that for the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:48.79,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.36,Main,Child,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:53.50,Thoughts,Nami,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!  This definitely sounds like kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:57.90,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,So you were brought here by strangers,\Nand didn't even talk to your parents first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.75,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You know what this sounds like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You were suffering from a {\i1}really{\i0} terrible illness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.24,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Are you a complete moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.89,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Is all this running too much for any of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.26,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'll carry anyone who's worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:13.99,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But you've already been here more than a year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.08,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Chopper, have a look at them after this.\NThen we'll know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.63,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sure.  Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.31,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.77,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.94,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.61,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.32,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You've gotten really powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.32,Secondary,Child,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.55,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,You're so cool, Raccoon Dog-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.25,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm not a raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But you just acted like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:46.95,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.99,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Chopper, lend me your fur coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:53.60,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:54.79,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Wait, I can't take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.75,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What is this place?  Are we outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:19:59.46,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Or maybe a freezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.85,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's so dark, I can't really tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.64,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This climate's perfect for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.34,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's so dark, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Oh, now I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.98,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,There's a door at the other end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.06,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.55,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Let's keep going!  This isn't a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.68,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.77,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Lady!  I don't wanna go in there!  It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.57,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.28,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What's wrong, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.06,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Hurry up!  They're still after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.88,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,They took me through here\Nwhen I first came to this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.29,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Really?  Then it must lead to the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.31,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,It's pretty cold, but try to bear it everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.03,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.48,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.67,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.55,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,around us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:52.64,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Around us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:57.56,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,There's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.03,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,inside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:14.19,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,I'm scared of this place\Nbecause there are frozen people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:16.40,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Huh?!  What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.08,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Frozen... corpses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:22.12,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,They're above us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:24.04,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,And under us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.59,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,{\i1}Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:34.10,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Ah!  Please, wait!  Don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Well, that takes care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:40.15,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,438)}Inside the laboratory ・ Biscuits Room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:40.15,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,479)}-Sanji's Group-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:38.40,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.15,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You've blocked their way.  That's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:41.85,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Let's keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:45.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I just felt a surge of emotion from Nami-san's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.74,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,She may have realized her feelings for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.53,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Still, what {\i1}are{\i0} these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.02,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,They have sheep legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Isn't there some kind of mythical creature like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:59.14,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There's no point worrying about them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:01.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,They'll have to wait\Nuntil we know what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:02.50,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.05,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Leave me!  I will remain here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:08.76,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I saw no sign of my son\Namong the children you helped escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:11.66,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,There must be other rooms!\NI should remain and search{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:14.41,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And how are you planning to move around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:18.65,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Leaving you behind\Nwould be the same as abandoning you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.36,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It would leave me with a terrible aftertaste!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:23.81,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,But I came here to save my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.55,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You're such an annoying bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:30.86,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Just ask us!  Say "Please search for my body"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:32.74,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Where is your body anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:36.91,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I refuse to be indebted to a pirate! \N I would sooner die than ask for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.98,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,H-However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:43.34,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,if you were to search for my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:46.34,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I would not complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:47.83,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Damn this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.83,0:22:50.01,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why is a detached head\Nacting like he's better than me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.87,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You intend to use violence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:53.67,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I-I have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:56.43,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I will not beg villains for my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:58.03,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:01.52,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Would crushing a defenseless head really make you feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:07.25,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The moment that you took him out of the cell,\Nyou'd already lost, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.19,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:14.04,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,This guy is really getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:17.27,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I was a fool to admire his resolve,\Neven if it was just for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.62,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I don't wanna help him any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:24.24,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Alas, I would be defenseless if you left me here,\Nbut if you want to take me with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:26.24,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I would not complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:34.15,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Damn... I'm gonna get you for this once you get your body back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:38.52,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You show no mercy, even to a detached head.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.94,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Yes.  I should be careful what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:43.96,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I wonder if Nami and the others have found an exit? \NLet's go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:45.94,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Damn it, that itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:53.48,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,543)}Main entrance to the laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.00,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hello?  My name is Monkey D. Luffy! {Copy-paste from 579}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:01.03,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm the man who's gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:02.86,Flashbacks,Usopp,0,0,0,,You answered too soon, and you're saying too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:05.86,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,Please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:06.68,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:10.15,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,It's freezing... Is that you, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:11.78,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,No, I'm not your boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.78,0:24:16.47,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,My companions keep getting cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.62,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,The samurai's gonna kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:20.12,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:23.52,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,Somebody please save me, I don't care who. {This one line is from 580's recap.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:25.12,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,I'm on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:27.34,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,Punk Hazard! {End copy-paste from 579}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.17,0:24:33.90,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,The name of the island,\Nplus the mention of the cold climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.90,0:24:38.85,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it,\Nthis call was sent from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.19,0:24:44.03,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,You know Straw Hat Luffy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.40,0:24:48.11,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no... {Not bothering with copy-pasting here because it's all just attack-names and one generic remark anyway.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:49.61,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,Fuusen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:50.91,Flashbacks,Kid,0,0,0,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.16,0:24:53.49,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.20,0:24:55.37,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.92,0:24:59.97,Flashbacks,Marine,0,0,0,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.96,0:25:06.78,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Two years ago, during the incident\Nwith the Celestial Dragons from the Roswald House,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.78,0:25:09.94,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,you, Kid, and Luffy worked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.39,0:25:13.05,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,What's more, during the great war...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:16.43,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Bring Straw-Hatter over here! {Copy-paste from 487}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.43,0:25:19.14,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take him away from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.14,0:25:21.15,Flashbacks,Law,0,0,0,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.64,0:25:25.96,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,When Straw Hat was being pursued by Akainu...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.96,0:25:27.58,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,you helped him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.62,0:25:35.16,Main,Law,0,0,0,,What business do you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:40.36,Main,Law,0,0,0,,False distress calls is your specialty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:45.54,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\Nthis transmission wasn't one of our traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.54,0:25:49.42,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Quite a mystery.  But I don't know anything,\Nso this conversation is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.42,0:25:53.94,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Cut the crap.  Let us into the laboratory!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.94,0:25:57.53,Main,Law,0,0,0,,It's my vacation home now.  I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.53,0:26:02.24,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Is it so wrong for a pirate like me\Nto stay on an island that you've abandoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:04.63,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I'm the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.63,0:26:09.20,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If Straw Hat does show up, you can have his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.20,0:26:11.99,Main,Law,0,0,0,,If that's all you want, then you should leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:20.45,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Those frozen people were so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.45,0:26:22.92,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.92,0:26:24.91,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Look!  There's a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.91,0:26:25.88,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We can get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.88,0:26:27.40,Main,Child,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.65,0:26:34.27,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,There's someone in there after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.89,0:26:38.82,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.82,0:26:40.65,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,We're out!  It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.32,0:26:46.43,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,We're out of the building!  We can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.43,0:26:48.46,Main,Child,0,0,0,,I can see Papa and Mama again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.46,0:26:50.08,Main,Child,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:52.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.25,0:26:55.44,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Tank is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.44,0:26:58.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Out of the way!  Out of the way!  Super-out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.67,0:27:01.82,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I will crush anyone who's in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.42,0:27:05.12,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,But I will avoid crushing flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:08.93,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The just a little kindhearted, Franky Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.93,0:27:12.70,Main,Crowd,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.64,0:27:19.15,Thoughts,Marine,0,0,0,,I can't tell what's the weirdest!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:24.63,Thoughts,Marine,0,0,0,,A giant raccoon dog, a winter bikini,\Ngiant kids, a robot, or a detached head...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.63,0:27:26.36,Thoughts,Marine,0,0,0,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.62,0:27:29.23,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I've seen you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.23,0:27:31.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Yeah!  It's the guy from Sabaody!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.62,0:27:34.58,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Were you the one who imprisoned these kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.58,0:27:37.84,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You scum!  We're not giving them back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:40.25,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.25,0:27:44.13,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Of all the atrocious fiends to run into... it's Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.13,0:27:46.93,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And with him is always a {\i1}cutie-swaaan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.93,0:27:49.85,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,This isn't good!  We've run into the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:52.47,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We can't go this way!  We'll have to find another exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.47,0:27:53.73,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hurry back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.19,0:27:59.21,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Quickly kids!  Through to the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.21,0:28:00.55,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There's gotta be a back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.55,0:28:03.27,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What's the Navy doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.27,0:28:05.26,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,How should I know?!  Anyway, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.15,0:28:09.21,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,Huh?  Isn't the Navy supposed to be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.21,0:28:10.43,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I suppose.  You can go to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.43,0:28:13.66,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,No way!  They look like gangsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.42,0:28:18.21,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,They're here, aren't they?!  Alone, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:22.08,Main,Law,0,0,0,,They were indeed here... to my surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.00,0:28:26.00,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Soldiers!  We will capture the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.96,0:28:30.04,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Right, let's go!  Follow the Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.09,0:28:32.17,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.13,0:28:42.57,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Is everyone alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.17,0:28:50.75,Main,Law,0,0,0,,They've made things {\i1}much{\i0} more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.34,0:29:09.73,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,The warship is floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.73,0:29:12.03,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Even the river is floating with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.03,0:29:14.80,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.25,0:29:19.10,Main,Law,0,0,0,,I can't let you leave this island anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.75,0:29:22.71,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Sorry that I said there wasn't anyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.72,0:29:26.14,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,This guy's bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.14,0:29:28.01,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.61,0:29:33.75,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,You can't lay a finger on him... He'd just pull it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.50,0:29:39.69,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.69,0:29:42.20,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Show him the power of G-5!
